    "boundary_note": "Where a 2026 seat merges two old seats (e.g. Cathcart + Pollok), it maps to the principal old seat. Where a 2026 seat is genuinely new (Glasgow Central, Bathgate, Edinburgh Northern), it maps to the closest geographical predecessor."
